---
interface Props {
  whatsappUrl: string;
}
const { whatsappUrl } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="como-funciona" class="relative bg-neutral-950 text-white py-20 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern opacity-[0.03]"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-[20%] w-[40%] h-[50%] bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_bottom,_rgba(250,204,21,0.08)_0%,_transparent_70%)]"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 scroll-reveal">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-yellow-400"></div>
      <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-yellow-400/80">La solución</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black leading-[0.95] tracking-tight scroll-reveal" style="--d:50ms">
        Antes hacías<br/>todo tú.<br/>
        <span class="text-stroke-yellow">Ahora no.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="flex items-end scroll-reveal" style="--d:100ms">
        <div class="space-y-4 text-neutral-500 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          <p><strong class="text-white">Antes:</strong> te llegaba un mensaje, dejabas lo que estabas haciendo, respondías, cotizabas, agendabas.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-white">Ahora:</strong> te llega una notificación que dice quién es, qué necesita, y a qué hora es la reunión.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 scroll-reveal" style="--d:200ms">
      <div class="spotlight-card group relative p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 border border-neutral-800 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden" data-spotlight>
        <div class="spotlight-glow"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-transparent scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
        <span class="text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-neutral-800 group-hover:text-yellow-400/20 transition-colors duration-500 leading-none relative">01</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-4 relative">Te encuentran cuando te buscan</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed text-sm relative">Alguien googlea "abogado laboral Santiago" o "dentista cerca". Apareces tú, no tu competencia. Web profesional, rápida, con WhatsApp integrado y optimizada para que Google te muestre primero.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="spotlight-card group relative p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 border border-neutral-800 border-t-0 md:border-t md:border-l-0 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden" data-spotlight>
        <div class="spotlight-glow"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-transparent scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
        <span class="text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-neutral-800 group-hover:text-yellow-400/20 transition-colors duration-500 leading-none relative">02</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-4 relative">Respondes en 30 segundos. Aunque estés durmiendo</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed text-sm relative">Un asistente en WhatsApp (número dedicado para tu negocio) que responde consultas, califica al cliente y agenda reuniones. A las 3am, en feriados, los domingos. Tú ves todo en un panel: quién escribió, qué necesita, si vale la pena.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="spotlight-card group relative p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 border border-neutral-800 border-t-0 md:border-t md:border-l-0 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden" data-spotlight>
        <div class="spotlight-glow"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-transparent scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left"></div>
        <span class="text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-neutral-800 group-hover:text-yellow-400/20 transition-colors duration-500 leading-none relative">03</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-4 relative">Sabes exactamente cuánto cuesta cada cliente</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed text-sm relative">Nada de "impresiones" ni "alcance". Google Ads y Meta Ads con tracking real: cuántos clientes llegaron, de dónde, y cuánto costó cada uno. Si no rinde, ajustamos. Si rinde, escalamos.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 text-center scroll-reveal" style="--d:300ms">
      <a href={whatsappUrl} target="_blank" data-wa-cta class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-neutral-500 hover:text-yellow-400 font-medium px-8 py-4 border border-neutral-800 hover:border-yellow-400/30 transition-all text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        Quiero esto para mi negocio
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Spotlight cursor-follow glow (Linear/Vercel style) */
  .spotlight-card {
    --mx: -100px;
    --my: -100px;
  }
  .spotlight-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(
      500px circle at var(--mx) var(--my),
      rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.07),
      transparent 40%
    );
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .spotlight-card:hover .spotlight-glow {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>
